    "description": "Aditya Birla Finance is actively seeking a talented and motivated Senior Financial Analyst to join our dynamic team in Ghaziabad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Aditya Birla Finance:\nAditya Birla Finance is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aditya Birla Finance!",
